gmx:name.gco:CharacterString: Feature Catalog for the 2016 Address Range-Feature County-based

gmx:scope.gco:CharacterString: The Address Range-Feature County-based shapefiles contain the geospatial edge geometry and attributes of all unsuppressed address ranges for a county or county equivalent area.
